" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div><div class=\"gold-gradient h-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"page-hero\"><div class=\"gold-gradient h-1 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"container-site relative\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" data-variant=\"default\" class=\"group/badge inline-flex h-5 w-fit shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border px-2 py-0.5 whitespace-nowrap transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3! [a]:hover:bg-primary/80 mb-4 bg-white/10 text-[#F5C200] border-[#F5C200]/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold\">About Us</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-balance max-w-4xl\">About the Mission</h1><p class=\"text-blue-200 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-3xl leading-relaxed\">A spiritual and philanthropic centre rooted in the teachings of Sri Ramakrishna and Swami Vivekananda, dedicated to the upliftment of the Abujhmaria tribal community since 1985.</p></div></section><section class=\"section bg-white\"><div class=\"container-site grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-start\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0D2660] mb-5\">Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama, Narayanpur</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama Narayanpur (RKMN) is a branch centre of <strong>Ramakrishna Math and Ramakrishna Mission</strong>, headquartered at Belur Math, West Bengal. Established on <strong>2 August 1985</strong>, the Ashrama was set up to serve the tribals of the remote Abujhmarh jungle in Narayanpur district, Chhattisgarh.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed\">The Abujhmarh region — meaning “unknown highlands” — spans about 4,000 sq. km. and is home to roughly 34,000 Abujhmaria tribals across 230+ far-flung villages. These tribals, categorised as a<!-- --> <strong>Particularly Vulnerable Tribal Group (PVTG)</strong> by the Government of India, had near-zero literacy and limited access to healthcare before the Mission arrived.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Today, RKMN serves <strong>200+ villages</strong> through education, healthcare, agricultural training, and rural development — uplifting thousands of lives each year in true Vivekananda spirit.<!-- --> <a class=\"text-[#0D2660] font-semibold hover:underline\" href=\"/about/history\">Read our full history →</a></p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4 text-[#C8201A]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#0D2660] uppercase\">Founded</span></div><p class=\"text-gray-800 font-medium text-sm\">2 August 1985</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-4 w-4 text-[#C8201A]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#0D2660] uppercase\">Affiliation</span></div><p class=\"text-gray-800 font-medium text-sm\">Belur Math, West Bengal</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-100 col-span-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award h-4 w-4 text-[#C8201A]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#0D2660] uppercase\">National Recognition</span></div><p class=\"text-gray-800 font-medium text-sm\">Indira Gandhi National Integration Award (2009)</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-2xl p-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm w-full\"><div class=\"relative w-44 h-44 drop-shadow-xl\"><img alt=\"Official Ramakrishna Mission Emblem\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"176px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Frkm-logo.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"devanagari text-xl text-[#C8201A] font-bold\">आत्मनो मोक्षार्थं जगद्धिताय च</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 italic mt-1\">For one&#x27;s own salvation and for the welfare of the world</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">— Swami Vivekananda</p></div></div><div class=\"navy-gradient text-white rounded-2xl p-7 w-full\"><p class=\"text-[#F5C200] text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide mb-3\">The Emblem Explained</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-200\"><li><span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Wavy waters</span> — Karma Yoga (selfless action)</li><li><span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Lotus</span> — Bhakti Yoga (devotion)</li><li><span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Rising sun</span> — Jnana Yoga (knowledge)</li><li><span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Serpent</span> — Raja Yoga (meditation)</li><li><span class=\"text-white font-semibold\">Swan (Hamsa)</span> — Paramatman (Supreme Self)</li></ul><p class=\"text-xs text-blue-400 mt-3 italic\">Designed by Swami Vivekananda</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 bg-white border-t border-blue-50\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-center mb-3\">Our Inspiration</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-1