border-4 border-[#F5C200]/60 shadow-md mb-4 group-hover:border-[#F5C200] transition-colors\"><img alt=\"Swami Vivekananda\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"160px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fswami-vivekananda.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-lg group-hover:underline\">Swami Vivekananda</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#C8201A] font-medium\">The Patriot-Saint of India</p></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 bg-[#F0F4FF]\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-center mb-10\">Our Core Values</h2><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-7 border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#0D2660]/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"w-8 h-1 bg-[#C8201A] rounded mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] mb-2\">Man-Making Education</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Swami Vivekananda envisioned education that builds character, strength, and inner divinity — not mere information transfer. Every curriculum and activity at RKM Narayanpur is guided by this ideal.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-7 border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#0D2660]/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"w-8 h-1 bg-[#C8201A] rounded mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] mb-2\">Service as Worship</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">&quot;He who sees Shiva in the poor, in the weak, and in the diseased, really worships Shiva.&quot; All activities — teaching, healing — are performed as Seva, seeing the Divine in every human being.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-7 border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#0D2660]/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"w-8 h-1 bg-[#C8201A] rounded mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] mb-2\">Harmony of Faiths</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">The Mission, true to Sri Ramakrishna&#x27;s teaching, respects and serves people of all faiths and communities without distinction of caste, creed, or race.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-7 border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#0D2660]/30 transition-all\"><div class=\"w-8 h-1 bg-[#C8201A] rounded mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] mb-2\">Holistic Development</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">We nurture physical, mental, moral, and spiritual growth — through sports, cultural activities, vocational training, and value-based academic programmes.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"leadership\" class=\"py-16 px-4 bg-white scroll-mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-center mb-3\">Leadership &amp; Functionaries</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10\">Key office bearers of Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama, Narayanpur and the College.</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-lg\">Swami Vyaptananda</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#C8201A] font-medium mb-3\">Secretary</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Head of Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama, Narayanpur — overall administration of education, healthcare, and tribal welfare activities across Narayanpur and Abujhmarh.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-lg\">Principal</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#C8201A] font-medium mb-3\">Principal, Ramakrishna Mission College</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Academic leadership of undergraduate (FYUGP) programmes affiliated to Bastar University. Contact the admissions office for the current office bearer.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F4FF] rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-lg\">Admissions Office</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#C8201A] font-medium mb-3\">Admissions &amp; Student Services</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">rkm.narainpur@gmail.com · 07781-252251 · Narayanpur, Chhattisgarh 494661</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section section-alt\"><div class=\"container-site max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"sm:mb-10 md:mb-12 text-center mx-auto max-w-3xl mb-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0D2660] text-balance\">Journey Through the Years</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4 sm:space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-start\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-12 sm:w-14\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#0D2660] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-[10px] sm:text-xs shadow-md border-2 border-[#F5C200]\">1985</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0 bg-[#F0F4FF] border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama, Narainpur established as a branch centre of Belur Math; 42 acres received on lease; work begins in a shed on campus.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-start\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-12 sm:w-14\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#0D2660] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-[10px] sm:text-xs shadow-md border-2 border-[#F5C200]\">1986</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0 bg-[#F0F4FF] border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Vivekananda Vidyapeeth and the Tribal Youth Training Centre started; Hospital (OPD) and Mobile Dispensary inaugurated.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-start\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-12 sm:w-14\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#0D2660] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-[10px] sm:text-xs shadow-md border-2 border-[#F5C200]\">1989</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0 bg-[#F0F4FF] border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Indoor Hospital inaugurated, expanding free healthcare for the Abujhmaria tribal community.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-start\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-12 sm:w-14\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#0D2660] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-[10px] sm:text-xs shadow-md border-2 border-[#F5C200]\">1990</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0 bg-[#F0F4FF] border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 leadin